00:12:08,834 --> 00:12:11,176
gone to the bathroom in a movie for no reason.

220
00:12:12,177 --> 00:12:16,021
But we do have those heartfelt post-bathroom moments in real life.

221
00:12:17,203 --> 00:12:21,708
And that just never gets reflected in media because you have this limited linear plane

222
00:12:21,748 --> 00:12:23,489
on which to work and the juxtaposition.

223
00:12:24,349 --> 00:12:29,734
It just has a different meaning when it's been placed there for you by a director or

