00:18:48,792 --> 00:18:52,333
but they are ultimately kind of existing to wait for you.

314
00:18:52,874 --> 00:18:57,016
So we asked ourselves the question, what would the player experience be like in a game where

315
00:18:57,436 --> 00:19:01,978
no one waits for you, you have to keep up with them and listen to them and play in service

