00:19:13,366 --> 00:19:16,949
So we needed to create stories, enough of them with enough detail,

321
00:19:17,029 --> 00:19:19,170
that would populate a fully realized world,

322
00:19:19,551 --> 00:19:23,253
characterized by overlapping dialogue and confluences of action.

323
00:19:24,447 --> 00:19:28,769
And this is the question that we started with and that we still often get asked about the

324
00:19:28,789 --> 00:19:29,130
