331
00:19:49,283 --> 00:19:51,084
care ward with a bunch of old people.

332
00:19:51,615 --> 00:19:55,337
So satisfaction is not necessarily what she would be experiencing.

333
00:19:55,397 --> 00:19:59,180
And so as nerve wracking as it was, we wanted to create an experience that left

334
00:19:59,300 --> 00:20:02,321
room for boredom or frustration, or maybe even anger.

335
00:20:02,341 --> 00:20:06,544
And this was reflected back to us in a lot of the reviews we got.

336
00:20:07,404 --> 00:20:10,726
